{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place parsley leaves in mixing bowl and chop <nobr>3 sec\/speed 8<\/nobr>. Transfer to a bowl and set aside.","Place 50 g butter, onions, carrots and 2 shallots in mixing bowl then chop <nobr>5 sec\/speed 5<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula. Without measuring cup, sauté <nobr>5 min\/100°C\/speed <\/nobr>.","Add flour, beef stock, bouquet garni, salt and pepper then cook <nobr>15 min\/100°C\/\/speed 2<\/nobr>. Strain through a fine sieve into a bowl and set aside. Clean mixing bowl.","Place remaining 4 shallots in mixing bowl and chop <nobr>5 sec\/speed 5<\/nobr>.","Add thyme leaves, bay leaf, parsley stalks, peppercorns and red wine then reduce <nobr>20 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<\/nobr>. Strain through a fine sieve into a bowl."," <strong>Insert butterfly whisk<\/strong>. Place reduced wine mixture, reserved stock mixture, beef jus, 2 tsp reserved chopped parsley, lemon juice and remaining 50 g butter then heat <nobr>2 min\/80°C\/speed 2<\/nobr>. <strong>Remove butterfly whisk<\/strong>. Serve immediately to accompany red meat."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["5 - 6 sprigs fresh flat-leaf parsley, leaves and stalks separated","100 g butter, diced","100 g onions, quartered","50 g carrots, cut in pieces","6 shallots, halved","40 g plain flour","400 g beef stock","1 bouquet garni (thyme, parsley, bay leaf)","½ tsp fine sea salt","1 - 2 pinches ground black pepper, to taste","1 sprig fresh thyme, leaves only","1 fresh bay leaf","5 black peppercorns, crushed","500 g red wine","1 Tbsp beef jus","1 Tbsp lemon juice"]}],"id":"r102697","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-mKc-yaQ4rus\/XZaeGriqQkI\/AAAAAAAAgi0\/rdddqI9HhLU-pfCKmFpeGeSOCtltvJTFgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_Ph8oT4RPIyrhUe8s.png","title":"Bordelaise Sauce","publishedAt":"2016-09-05T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"2 g","fat":"14 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"7 g","calories":"775 kJ \/ 187 kcal"},"usefulItems":"fine sieve","hintsAndTricks":["Can also be made using white wine to accompany fish or chicken dishes."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","55m","6 portions"]}